About PBJ Fire

"Ensuring Safety, Securing Lives."

{/* Company Overview */}

Who We Are

PBJ Fire, established in 2019 in Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, is a **leading provider of fire safety solutions**. We specialize in **ISI & CE marked** fire-fighting equipment, consulting, and **turnkey installations**. Our goal is to ensure **uncompromised safety** through advanced **engineering, reliability, and customer-centric solutions**.

{/* Mission & Vision */}

Our Mission

To provide **comprehensive fire safety and surveillance solutions** that empower organizations, ensuring a secure environment through expert technology and precision.

Our Vision

To be **India’s most trusted fire safety partner**, setting benchmarks in safety innovation, reliability, and excellence across industries.

{/* Key People Section with Photos */} Shailesh Jadhav CEO & Founder A visionary leader with a **relentless commitment to fire safety**, Shailesh Jadhav founded PBJ Fire with the goal of **revolutionizing the industry**.

Under his leadership, PBJ Fire has grown into a **trusted name** across **government, commercial, and industrial sectors**. His belief? *Fire safety isn't just a service—it's a responsibility to protect lives and assets.* Bhuvanesh Manwatkar Pune Branch Manager Leading PBJ Fire’s **expansion into Pune**, Bhuvanesh ensures seamless service delivery.

His **technical expertise and strategic approach** have made PBJ Fire a trusted name in fire safety. With a passion for **innovation and efficiency**, he believes in **adapting global safety standards** to meet the **growing fire safety needs** of India's urban and industrial landscape. {/* Growth & Expansion */}

Our Growth Story

From **Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar** to **Pune and beyond**, PBJ Fire has secured **landmark projects** with top industries and institutions. Our work with **MGM University, Prozone Mall, PVR, INOX, and DRDO** showcases our **expertise in handling high-profile fire safety projects**. As we continue to grow, our focus remains on **quality, trust, and life-saving innovation**.
